<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="~/lib/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/umd/popper.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link href="~/lib/bootstrap/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Index</title>
    <style>
        .container-custom {
            width: 1900px;
            height: 2500px;
            overflow: scroll;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .color-rectangle {
            width: 1900px;
            height: 765px;
            background-color: #538AC6;
        }

        .image-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .centered-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            max-width: 1500px;
            max-height: 100%;
        }

        .text-container {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            right: 10%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            text-align: left;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #000;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 30px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .bold-text {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 65px;
        }

        /* New container styles */
        .new-container {
            width: 960px;
            height: 276px;
            background-color: #F5F7FA;
            margin: 0 auto;
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .new-container .inner-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .get-started-text {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 48px;
            white-space: nowrap; /* Prevent line break */
        }

        .quote-text {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .rectangle-button {
            width: 157px;
            height: 44px;
            background-color: #1574D2;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        /* Updated Navbar styles */
        header {
            background-color: #ECECE9; /* Updated background color */
            height: 60px;
            width: 1900px; /* Set the navbar width to 1900px */
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            margin-left: 30px;
            height: 60px;
        }

        .menu {
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: 30px; /* Added margin to the right side */
        }

        .lih {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 20px;
            padding: 10px 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; /* Updated font family */
            color: black; /* Updated text color */
        }

        .lih:hover {
            background-color: #1574D2;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="~/images/anotherchance.png" height="100%" alt="Logo">
    </div>

    <div class="menu">
        <div class="ul">
            <div class="li lih">About</div>
            <div class="li lih">Resources</div>
            <div class="li lih">Jobs</div>
            <div class="li lih">
                <a asp-controller="AppUser" asp-action="LoginAppUser">Login</a>
            </div>
            <div class="li lih">
                <a asp-controller="AppUser" asp-action="CreateAppUser">Sign up</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>
<div class="container-custom">
    <div class="color-rectangle">
        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="~/images/handshake.jpg" alt="Centered Image" class="centered-image">
            <div class="text-container">
                <p class="bold-text">You always <br> deserve another <br> chance</p>
                <p>Embrace new beginnings and seize every <br> opportunity. AnotherChance opens doors, <br> connecting dreams with possibilities, and <br> empowering individuals to rewrite their story.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="new-container">
        <div class="inner-content">
            <div class="get-started-text">GET STARTED HERE</div>
            <div class="quote-text">
                Just because someone stumbles and loses their way, it doesnâ€™t mean they are lost forever<br>
                - Professor X
            </div>
            <!-- Rectangle button -->
            <div class="rectangle-button">GET STARTED</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
